OL,6,FThe is one of the biggest nights in
OL,7,Fthe Bailiwicks' sporting calendar as
OL,8,Fit brings together local athletes,
OL,9,Fcoaches and volunteers.
OL,11,FIt is an opportunity to celebrate
OL,12,Findividual and group achievements, as
OL,13,Fwell as all the people who are
OL,14,Finvolved in making sport across the
OL,15,FChannel Islands possible.
