OL,3,CHow do I watch the 2023 Betway CI
OL,4,CSports Awards and can I get involved?
OL,6,FThere will be two special half-hour
OL,7,Flive programmes shown on ITV1 across
OL,8,Fthe Channel Islands on Thursday 8
OL,9,FFebruary. The first starts at 8:30pm
OL,10,Fwith the second at 10:45pm. Both will
OL,11,Fbe uploaded to ITV Channel's shortly
OL,12,Fafter they are broadcast.
OL,14,FThis year's event is being held at
OL,15,FBeau Sejour in Guernsey after the last
OL,16,Fceremony took place in Jersey.
